    public static enum AgentLoader.StandardAgentLoaderType
extends java.lang.Enum<AgentLoader.StandardAgentLoaderType>
    Standard types of loaders for agents. The name of the loader is used in the agent description in the scenario file.
    Author:
    Andrei Olaru

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • ADF2

        public static final AgentLoader.StandardAgentLoaderType ADF2
        The agent is described by means of an .adf2 file. The ADF2 agent is a special kind of CompositeAgent, with some pre-configured components. An S-CLAIM agent can be easily loaded as a COMPOSITE agent. This enumeration value is kept only for backwards compatibility of scenarios.

      • COMPOSITE

        public static final AgentLoader.StandardAgentLoaderType COMPOSITE
        The agent is a CompositeAgent that is made up of various components.

      • JAVA

        public static final AgentLoader.StandardAgentLoaderType JAVA
        The agent is described by means of traditional Java code. Currently unimplemented.
